{"ok":true,"module":"io/input/i01","docs":{"io/input/i01/binding_port":{"type":"UInt16","label_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.binding_port.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.binding_port.help","enum_set":"flowio_binding_port_digital_input","label":"Port physique I01","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.binding_port.label","help":"Identifiant du port physique utilise par l'entree digitale I01. La valeur reference un binding compile-time autorise, pas un numero de GPIO brut.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.binding_port.help"},"io/input/i01/counter_total":{"type":"Float","label_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.counter_total.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.counter_total.help","label":"Cumul compteur","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.counter_total.label","help":"Valeur cumulée éditable pour I01 en mode compteur. Cette correction écrase immédiatement le total actuel du compteur, devient la nouvelle statistique long terme et est écrite immédiatement en NVS.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.counter_total.help"},"io/input/i01/edge_mode":{"type":"UInt8","label_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.edge_mode.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.edge_mode.help","enum_set":"flowio_edge_mode","label":"Mode de front I01","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.edge_mode.label","help":"Front a compter pour I01 en mode compteur (0=descendant, 1=montant, 2=les deux).","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.edge_mode.help"},"io/input/i01/i01_active_high":{"type":"Bool","label_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_active_high.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_active_high.help","label":"Actif a 1 I01","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_active_high.label","help":"Si active, l'entrée I01 est consideree active a l'etat haut.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_active_high.help"},"io/input/i01/i01_c0":{"type":"Float","label_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_c0.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_c0.help","label":"Coefficient C0 I01","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_c0.label","help":"Coefficient multiplicateur applique au nombre d'impulsions de I01 en mode compteur. Il convertit les impulsions brutes en valeur cumulee publiee. Formule: value = c0 * impulsions.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_c0.help"},"io/input/i01/i01_name":{"type":"CharArray","label_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_name.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_name.help","label":"Nom entrée I01","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_name.label","help":"Nom lisible de l'entrée digitale I01.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_name.help"},"io/input/i01/i01_prec":{"type":"Int32","label_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_prec.label","help_t":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_prec.help","unit":"digits","label":"Precision I01","label_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_prec.label","help":"Nombre de decimales conservees pour la valeur calculee de I01 en mode compteur.","help_i18n":"cfgdocs.io.input.i01.i01_prec.help"},"io/input/i01/i01_pull_mode":{"enum_set":"io_digital_pull_mode"},"io/input/i01/mode":{"type":"UInt8","label_t":"cfgmods.io.input.i01.mode.label","help_t":"cfgmods.io.input.i01.mode.help","enum_set":"flowio_digital_input_mode","label":"Mode entrée I01","label_i18n":"cfgmods.io.input.i01.mode.label","help":"Choisit le type de fonctionnement de I01 (Etat ou Compteur d'Impulsion). Changement pris en compte au redemarrage.","help_i18n":"cfgmods.io.input.i01.mode.help"}},"meta":{}}